channel.description:
Pastor Paul Begley is a pastor from Indiana that gives you current events and how they relate to the Bible

We always offer a call to salvation and Jesus is adding to the church daily.
We offer free Bibles to new converts!
We send free  anointed prayer cloths, prayer blankets and chemo caps to those who need a healing.
If you feel led to help with the postage or the broadcasting costs you can donate at: PayPal.me/DonatePastorBegley

Coming Apocalypse air live  Mon - Fri 12p - 2pm ET
                              And Sunday night Live 7p - 10pm ET

Coming Apocalypse airs on Direct TV 367 Fri 11:30pm ET

http://www.paulbegleyprophecy.com 
Like my fb @ http://www.facebook.com/Paul.begley.37
Follow me on Twitter pastorbegley
Follow me on Periscope Pastorbegley
